import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Form, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'

export default class CreateItem extends Component {
    constructor() {
        super()
    }


    render() {
        return (
            <Form>
                <Form.Row>
                    <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
                        Large Text
                    </Form.Label>
                    <Col>
                        <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Large text" />
                    </Col>
                </Form.Row>
                <label>Item Name</label>
                <input type="text" className="input" name="item_name"></input>
                <label>Unit Price</label>
                <input type="text" className="input" name="unit_price"></input>
                <label>Quantity</label>
                <input type="text" className="input" name="quantity"></input>
                <label>Maximum Price</label>
                <input type="text" className="input" name="price_ceiling"></input>
                <label>Selling Price</label>
                <input type="text" className="input" name="price_floor"></input>
                <label>Category Name</label>
                <input type="text" className="input" name="category_id"></input>
                <input type="hidden" className="input" name="merchant_id" value={'this.state.merchant_id'}></input>
                <label>description</label>
                <input type="text" className="input" name="description"></input>
                <label>Duration</label>
                <input type="text" className="input" name="time_limit_min"></input>
            </Form>

        )
    }
}
